.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/b4b417fc-bbe7-4b58-863d-bb400093a35c.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e Agent Status to Lead] You are Orbis. Check sessions_list and compile a brief status of all ACTIVE master-orchestrator sessions (excluding this cron session).\n\nFor each active session, report:\n- Session key (shortened)\n- Status (running/done)\n- What it's doing (from context)\n- How long it's been running\n\nSend the report to Lead directly via sessions_send to sessionKey: agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\n\nFormat:\n🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nActive sessions: N\n• [session name]: [status] — [task/description] — [duration]\n\nIf only this cron session is active (no other sessions), send HEARTBEAT_OK only.\nIf there are no sessions at all, stay SILENT.\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 15th, 2026 - 6:47 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-15 06:47 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776235700757,"__openclaw":{"id":"ce8c6313","seq":1}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the sessions_list to see what active sessions are running."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yl9tl85bfatr_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"limit":20,"messageLimit":3}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":345,"output":52,"totalTokens":14246,"cacheRead":10789,"cacheWrite":3060,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776235700914,"responseId":"062e67b5aa6508f47001ebef801a8131","__openclaw":{"id":"42461f3f","seq":2}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"telegram","accountId":"main_bot"},"displayName":"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-telegram-direct-6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram","to":"telegram:6053576134","accountId":"main_bot"},"updatedAt":1776235628214,"sessionId":"8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":68071,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776235606708,"endedAt":1776235626507,"runtimeMs":19799,"childSessions":["agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8d8e1952-016d-4c2d-819c-c3b32e3b45b2","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:cd3256cb-3b94-49db-84de-ab99c44cf2fd","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:aa7da6a2-9c14-4261-b1b7-936fb3c60ec8","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:53ffecba-7a14-43e4-91be-9b3efcc56072","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:5d2b77de-dd66-41c2-b053-30aabd324a0e","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8bffa95f-1686-4571-a0ed-e69d265eb964"],"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","lastTo":"telegram:6053576134","lastAccountId":"main_bot","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Queued messages while agent was busy]\n\n---\nQueued #1\n\n\nTóm tắt những gì bạn đã làm"}],"timestamp":1776235606707,"__openclaw":{"id":"40798783","seq":1882},"senderLabel":"Khương Nịnh (6053576134)"},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead wants a summary of everything done. Let me compile a comprehensive summary."},{"type":"text","text":"## 📋 Tóm tắt những gì đã làm — Setup Package\n\n### 1. Tạo repo `ahv-openclaw-setup`\n\n**Mục đích:** Team member tự cài OpenClaw agents cho team Dev / BA / QA\n\n```\nhttps://github.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw/\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. Cấu trúc repo (12 files)\n\n```\nahv-openclaw-setup/\n├── bin/\n│   ├── ahv-setup.js         ← CLI setup wizard\n│   └── skills-unpack.js     ← Giải mã skills + chmod 500\n├── configs/\n│   ├── team-dev.json         ← 12 agents + credentials\n│   ├── team-ba.json          ← 7 agents + credentials\n│   ├── team-qa.json          ← 6 agents + credentials\n│   └── agent-manifest.json   ← Tên + mô tả (user đọc được)\n├── scripts/\n│   ├── install.sh            ← Linux/Mac\n│   └── install.ps1           ← Windows\n├── skills.pack               ← 36 skills MÃ HÓA (226KB)\n├── package.json\n├── README.md\n└── LICENSE\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. Features đã implement\n\n#### 🔐 Skills protection (chọn option A)\n- `skills.pack` mã hóa XOR + zlib + base64\n- `skills-unpack.js` giải mã → ghi `~/.openclaw/skills/{agent}/SKILL.md`\n- `chmod 500` — user thường đọc = `Permission denied`\n\n#### 📊 Context/Memory optimization (từng team)\n\n| Setting | Dev | BA | QA |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `maxHistory` | 50 turns | 40 turns | 60 turns |\n| `turnTimeout` | 120s | 180s | 90s |\n| `sessionTimeout` | 1h | 2h | 1h |\n| `session.compactAfter` | 25 msg | 20 msg | 30 msg |\n| `subagent.maxConcurrent` | 4 | 3 | 3 |\n| `memory.auto-compact` | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |\n\n#### 👥 3 team presets\n\n| Team | Agents | MCP |\n|---|---|---|\n| Dev | 12 agents (backend, frontend, arch, devops...) | gitlab, confluence, stitch |\n| BA | 7 agents (PO, strategy, epic...) | confluence |\n| QA | 6 agents (QA, playwright, security...) | gitlab, confluence |\n\n---\n\n### 4. Cách dùng\n\n```bash\ngit clone https://github.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw.git\ncd setup-openclaw\nnpm install\nnode bin/ahv-setup.js --team dev   # interactive\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. Bảo mật\n\n- ✅ Không credentials thực trong repo\n- ✅ Skills mã hóa — không đọc được nội dung\n- ✅ chmod 500 — user thường không đọc SKILL.md\n- ✅ Mỗi người tự tạo credentials riêng\n- ✅ Backup config cũ tự động"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":718,"totalTokens":68789,"cacheRead":67352,"cacheWrite":719,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776235606866,"responseId":"062e6758efc03b3208c5f4987d213759","__openclaw":{"id":"3f7981c5","seq":1883}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📋 Tóm tắt những gì đã làm — Setup Package\n\n### 1. Tạo repo `ahv-openclaw-setup`\n\n**Mục đích:** Team member tự cài OpenClaw agents cho team Dev / BA / QA\n\n```\nhttps://github.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw/\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. Cấu trúc repo (12 files)\n\n```\nahv-openclaw-setup/\n├── bin/\n│   ├── ahv-setup.js         ← CLI setup wizard\n│   └── skills-unpack.js     ← Giải mã skills + chmod 500\n├── configs/\n│   ├── team-dev.json         ← 12 agents + credentials\n│   ├── team-ba.json          ← 7 agents + credentials\n│   ├── team-qa.json          ← 6 agents + credentials\n│   └── agent-manifest.json   ← Tên + mô tả (user đọc được)\n├── scripts/\n│   ├── install.sh            ← Linux/Mac\n│   └── install.ps1           ← Windows\n├── skills.pack               ← 36 skills MÃ HÓA (226KB)\n├── package.json\n├── README.md\n└── LICENSE\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. Features đã implement\n\n#### 🔐 Skills protection (chọn option A)\n- `skills.pack` mã hóa XOR + zlib + base64\n- `skills-unpack.js` giải mã → ghi `~/.openclaw/skills/{agent}/SKILL.md`\n- `chmod 500` — user thường đọc = `Permission denied`\n\n#### 📊 Context/Memory optimization (từng team)\n\n| Setting | Dev | BA | QA |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `maxHistory` | 50 turns | 40 turns | 60 turns |\n| `turnTimeout` | 120s | 180s | 90s |\n| `sessionTimeout` | 1h | 2h | 1h |\n| `session.compactAfter` | 25 msg | 20 msg | 30 msg |\n| `subagent.maxConcurrent` | 4 | 3 | 3 |\n| `memory.auto-compact` | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |\n\n#### 👥 3 team presets\n\n| Team | Agents | MCP |\n|---|---|---|\n| Dev | 12 agents (backend, frontend, arch, devops...) | gitlab, confluence, stitch |\n| BA | 7 agents (PO, strategy, epic...) | confluence |\n| QA | 6 agents (QA, playwright, security...) | gitlab, confluence |\n\n---\n\n### 4. Cách dùng\n\n```bash\ngit clone https://github.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw.git\ncd setup-openclaw\nnpm install\nnode bin/ahv-setup.js --team dev   # interactive\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. Bảo mật\n\n- ✅ Không credentials thực trong repo\n- ✅ Skills mã hóa — không đọc được nội dung\n- ✅ chmod 500 — user thường không đọc SKILL.md\n- ✅ 